{"tid":1283234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致怯緊嘅中學生、大專生、出左社會的","createTime":"2019-07-03T17:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:31:27.000Z","uid":267007,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e83f1155f698f208fa13fe70eb387026398434d1","tid":1283234,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:58:40.000Z","msg":"已經有好多post教你有人上門要點做<br />\n不詳談了<br />\n但我想講嘅係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我唔想叫你唔好驚！<br />\n我想你知道<br />\n你而家恐懼、害怕</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係正常的</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>唔好以為自己覺得驚 = 唔夠勇<br />\n你走到而家已經係勇士！！<br />\n記得準備好萬一有人上門要點做<br />\n同時唔好怕同身邊同路人分享同抒發心情<br />\n因為有適當嘅陪伴會抒緩到內心嘅不安！<br />\n<br />\n最後請記得<br />\n怯呢種感覺唔係某年齡層嘅福利<br />\n唔好怕瘀而收埋<br />\n你身邊都有好多同樣怯緊嘅同伴<br />\n你唔係唯一！<br />\n<br />\n我地全部都係你嘅同路人<br />\n我地全部都係你嘅聆聽者<br />\nWe will stand with you as one!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b61892097e5f26d3e1f1c0e3d376fcd6f5b15bc6","tid":1283234,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e629eac705b652245e01e2cf17a5288e3d1ff001","tid":1283234,"uid":218914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:05:36.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"c4149d18286855c6f55947e467ef7d31992ae6db","tid":1283234,"uid":262737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:06:03.000Z","msg":"「我冇野講<br />\n我要搵律師，（畀律師電話我）」<br />\n<br />\n電話唔解鎖<br />\n唔簽任何文件<br />\n唔信任何警察"},{"pid":"5925e197d3a5762e1f2cf0b9be7a382499632ba1","tid":1283234,"uid":36380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a15bbf817651eec79dc608255618a10e780acac","tid":1283234,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:06:41.000Z","